org.graffiti.plugin.parameter

Interface ParameterList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Displayable, Parameter

    public interface ParameterList
extends Parameter
    A ParameterList can be used to create enumeration type parameters, by grouping them into a list. The list can contain any number of SingleParameters.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.4 $
